Task Manager Application (Intermediate):
Description: Build a task manager application where users can create, update, and delete tasks.
Tasks can have due dates, priority levels, and labels. Include authentication to allow users to have their own task lists.
Tech Stack: MongoDB, Express.js, React, Node.js (MERN stack), JWT for authentication.

